  "",
  "Hell, for now, chose rolling dunes.",
  "",
  "Alice longed for sunlight.",
  "Her eyes had adjusted now to the dim, though they ached from squinting.",
  "She rubbed her temples and hoped she’d grow used to this eternal dusk.",
  "",
  "Around twenty minutes later, they crossed under a bridge.",
