  "Supposedly it glides across dark waters and extends a plank to shore.",
  "They’ll be waiting for you there.",
  "They’ll help you board.”",
  "",
  "“And then?”",
  "",
  "“And then they offer you the draft of the Lethe, brewed by the Lady Meng Po herself.” Moore’s eyes grew distant.",
  "The lopsided smile sagged off his face.",
  "“They say it tastes of dandelions, of dewdrops at dawn.",
  "You drink.",
