  "",
  "“Okay,” said Alice.",
  "“Let me see if I can get it all straight.",
  "A, you can only leave Pride once you pass.",
  "B, we have not passed.",
  "C, we must follow the rules of Hell.",
  "Therefore, Z, we cannot depart.",
  "Is that right?”",
  "",
  "“It’s obvious, dearie,” Moore scoffed.",
  "“Logic compels you.”",
  "",
  "“But I refuse again to accept the conclusion,” said Alice.",
  "“Why do A, B, and C lead to Z?”",
  "",
