"",
"The bone-things were most interested in Peter.",
"Alice they largely ignored; they skirted right past her to get to him.",
"They made short work of his cocoon, flinging shreds of fabric through the air.",
"He wrenched himself free and batted his hands around his head, trying to protect his face and neck.",
"But they would not stop coming.",
